description:
Web Proxy for Microsoft Windows is an enterprise-grade web filtering proxy and secure web gateway running natively on Microsoft Windows.

Web Proxy for Microsoft Windows is an enterprise-grade web filtering proxy and secure web gateway running natively on Microsoft Windows.
It can be easily integrated with Microsoft Active Directory on-premises or deployed directly in the Microsoft Azure cloud and work as Secure Web Proxy, decrypt HTTPS traffic, enforce Safe Browsing, protect from viruses and malware, filter HTTP requests and responses and inspect contents of HTML pages.
The application is installed natively on Microsoft Windows and can be managed by any administrator using Microsoft Management Console.
